Text: I'm a guy with a big dream in my mind, I live in a poor family in centre of
  Afghanistan, it's bamyan province that I live. After many years I get success to
  finish my degree. One Friday evening when I scroll down my face book suddenly a
  post catch my eyes that was travelling to Portugal....................................It
  was wonderful for me to visit Portugal and find out more about this country
